<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#2f2f4f">Originally posted by Lonzrick on 10-01-2000 01:03 AM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=10 COLS=45 WRAP="VIRTUAL">Since our FA weapon hasn't been found, I thought it would be amusing to poke some fun at Verant and what we *know* is going to happen.

We know that our "epic" weapon will be a time consuming piece of crap.  Verant never provides us with anything else.

We know that no matter how good the weapon may be, someone will complain and it will be nerfed to further uselessness.

So, let's have a contest.

I'm a master-blacksmith, so I'm gonna make two prizes for the two winners.

Contest 1: Predict the crappy stats.  Sumbit your prediction for the attack/delay and Wis bonus on the weapon.  I will tally up the differences and who ever has the smallest number wins.  (For instance, you predict 15/10 with +15 wisdom.  The stats are 9/45 +2 Wisdom.  That's 6+35+13=54 points.)

Contest 2: Predict the date of the nerf.  Whoever is closest wins.

Winner of Contest 1 gets a full set (well, the 8 pieces that show) of special "Nerficite Armor."  It's red like Rubicite, but had all the stats removed....Nerficite.  You can wear it or give it to your favorite Twink.

Winner of Contest 2 gets one Culture Breastplate.  I'm human, so can only make the Human sized one...but I'll use Imbued Diamond and Enchanted Platinum Bar.  Again, wear or give to your favorite Twink.

To register, contact me in the game.  I'm on almost all the time.  Lonzrick.  Go unanon so I can see you're a Cleric.  Tell me your predictions and I'll write them down.  Then I'll post the updates at my website..um...it'll be [URL=http://www.romeosquare.com/nerfemall.html]http://www.romeosquare.com/nerfemall.html[/URL]  .

This might be fun!

Lonzrick L'Amore
Povar</TEXTAREA>
